        "TileImage": "$($repository 78f98c70-b7be-4578-9b6a-1c96a3e1ff1a).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, 47. Your aim is to eliminate 3 targets: Dawood Rangan and Vanya Shah (we all know what for), as well as The Kashimirian, a local hitman attempting to become the world&apos;s best. The reason to eliminate him is to ensure your status of the best, because who knows what to expect from a man like him. Make sure the man dies in a falling object accident if possible; that would make doubly ironic. Also make sure you do it in your own suit to fully show your skill! Hint: first help The Kashimirian..",
